Corporate Social Responsibility

One Earth • One home • One obligation 
From energy conservation to community involvement, we are committed to preserving our Earth and all its dynamic, spirited inhabitants for future generations through the continued use of sustainable, renewable processes. 

Learn More








22 Locations, 4 Continents
Discover our diverse collection of hotels and resorts located around the world.
VIEW ALL LOCATIONS >


Previous
Next








The Langham, Sydney
Dramatic Harbour views. Quaint cobbled streets. Historic brick buildings. Discover a secluded tranquillity nestled in the heart of The Rocks district of metropolitan Sydney.


Discover More









The Langham, London
The Langham, London is Europe’s first Grand Hotel andan iconic landmark. Since 1865, it has captivated royalty, celebrities, musicians, and artists and continues to impress travellers with its legendary hotel heritage. Discover unmatched service and traditional elegance in one of the city’s most celebrated hotels.


Discover More









Langham Place, New York, Fifth Avenue
Sharp metropolitan style that inspires. Nestled in New York City’s midtown Manhattan on Fifth Avenue, the hotel is surrounded by some of the city’s most enduring landmarks. Explore the Empire State Building, Times Square, Grand Central Terminal and more, all just minutes from the hotel. 


Discover More









The Langham, Hong Kong
Vibrant, classical style that echoes the spirit of the city. Towering 16 storeys close to the fashionable Canton Road. From the hotel’s central location, enjoy easy access to top luxury brands and stunning harbour views. 


Discover More









The Langham, Shanghai, Xintiandi
A strikingly contemporary tower on the “Champs Elysees of the East.” Breathtaking panoramic views of the traditional Shikumen storefronts of Old Shanghai. A premier location near glamourous designer boutiques, art galleries, and exclusive restaurants.  


Discover More









The Langham, Chicago
An iconic landmark in the city’s skyline. Housed in a skyscraper designed by renowned architect Mies van der Rohe, it is mere minutes to the Loop, Grant Park, and the glittering Magnificent Mile. 


Discover More









The Langham, Sydney
Dramatic Harbour views. Quaint cobbled streets. Historic brick buildings. Discover a secluded tranquillity nestled in the heart of The Rocks district of metropolitan Sydney.
Discover More






The Langham, London
The Langham, London is Europe’s first Grand Hotel andan iconic landmark. Since 1865, it has captivated royalty, celebrities, musicians, and artists and continues to impress travellers with its legendary hotel heritage. Discover unmatched service and traditional elegance in one of the city’s most celebrated hotels.
Discover More






Langham Place, New York, Fifth Avenue
Sharp metropolitan style that inspires. Nestled in New York City’s midtown Manhattan on Fifth Avenue, the hotel is surrounded by some of the city’s most enduring landmarks. Explore the Empire State Building, Times Square, Grand Central Terminal and more, all just minutes from the hotel. 
Discover More






The Langham, Hong Kong
Vibrant, classical style that echoes the spirit of the city. Towering 16 storeys close to the fashionable Canton Road. From the hotel’s central location, enjoy easy access to top luxury brands and stunning harbour views. 
Discover More






The Langham, Shanghai, Xintiandi
A strikingly contemporary tower on the “Champs Elysees of the East.” Breathtaking panoramic views of the traditional Shikumen storefronts of Old Shanghai. A premier location near glamourous designer boutiques, art galleries, and exclusive restaurants.  
Discover More






The Langham, Chicago
An iconic landmark in the city’s skyline. Housed in a skyscraper designed by renowned architect Mies van der Rohe, it is mere minutes to the Loop, Grant Park, and the glittering Magnificent Mile. 
Discover More





















 













