Langham's Andrew Jessop Speaks with HVS Executive Search








































menuclose









Industry Update




Press Release 4 October 2011Langham's Andrew Jessop Speaks with HVS Executive Search


Watch an exclusive interview: Andrew Jessop, Vice President Development Worldwide for Langham Hotels International shares why this legendary company that dates back to 1865 is also the new kid on the block.Watch this exclusive interview to learn more about what makes Langham the new kid on the block. In an exclusive interview with HVS Executive Search Vice President Development Worldwide Andrew Jessop tells us more about why an owner should choose to partner with Langham their partners with Langham Hotels International. This legendary company dates back to 1865 but has only just signed their first hotel in the Middle East. Watch this exclusive interview to learn more about what makes Langham the new kid on the block.


About HVS
HVS, the world"s leading consulting and services organization focused on the hotel, mixed-use, shared ownership, gaming, and leisure industries, celebrated its 35th anniversary in 2015. Established in 1980, the company performs 4,500+ assignments each year for hotel and real estate owners, operators, and developers worldwide. HVS principals are regarded as the leading experts in their respective regions of the globe. Through a network of more than 35 offices and more than 500 professionals, HVS provides an unparalleled range of complementary services for the hospitality industry. HVS.com




